{"tid":2213911,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陸拒認海峽中線「如硬推港國安法」","createTime":"2020-09-23T01:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T01:44:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"00726cac292b8e9636ee86209700589dc94bfc28","tid":2213911,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T01:44:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200923/GUZWJCVQBBAOFKDIC6T6W5VKDQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200923%2FGUZWJCVQBBAOFKDIC6T6W5VKDQ%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I245RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=6c2438bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200923%2FGUZWJCVQBBAOFKDIC6T6W5VKDQ%2F&h=afac6014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200923/GUZWJCVQBBAOFKDIC6T6W5VKDQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n陸拒認海峽中線「如硬推港國安法」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/A1JJn7WohTWhvG6-qQe5Yvurdq0=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CH2QEZSITRCSROVQCPEWW2HNI4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FA1JJn7WohTWhvG6-qQe5Yvurdq0%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCH2QEZSITRCSROVQCPEWW2HNI4.jpg&h=b938e026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■蔡英文昨視察澎湖空軍部隊時，與各級官兵合照。<br />\n<br />\n台灣外長吳釗燮表示，中國大陸外交部否認海峽中線的存在，等同摧毀台海現狀，就像北京在香港強加《港區國安法》，摧毀香港的一國兩制。就連台灣前總統馬英九也「不認同」中方的說法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n象徵兩岸維持和平<br />\n<br />\n吳釗燮昨表示，海峽中線一直都是避免兩岸軍事衝突及維持台海和平的象徵，呼籲國際社會正視共機不斷跨越台海中線、破壞兩岸和平及威脅台灣民眾的事實，並予以強力譴責，並要求陸方停止施壓。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n所謂「海峽中線」是1950年代美國與中華民國簽訂《中美共同防禦條約》時，由美國太平洋司令部一名軍官戴維斯的軍官劃定海峽中線，因此又稱「戴維斯線」。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣 《蘋果新聞網》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FK7tebDMHiOF2XidkoRWCPCXthY=/627x889/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VL7TMNIZYFHMJC2G5XP37AZP2Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFK7tebDMHiOF2XidkoRWCPCXthY%3D%2F627x889%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVL7TMNIZYFHMJC2G5XP37AZP2Q.gif&h=87ab6006&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}